original_text: These are they that were numbered by Moses and Eleazar the priest, who numbered the children of Israel in the plains of Moab by Jordan near Jericho.
korean_text: 이는 모세와 제사장 엘르아살이 계수한 자라 그들이 여리고 맞은편 요단 가 모압 평지에서 이스라엘 자손을 계수한 중에는

sentences.original_text: These are they that were numbered
by Moses and Eleazar the priest
who numbered the children of Israel
